e\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s great she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s there and it will always be exciting and always bring some nice nerves,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d said Bol of her 24-year-old opponent.\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2715, \"end\": 2718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatian_Bol_Ladies_Open\", \"score\": 0.9900653542076041, \"rank\": 0.009818383644624245, \"text\": \"Bol\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatian_Bol_Ladies_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatian_Bol_Ladies_Open\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some nice nerves\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2705}, {\"ngram\": \"her 24-year-old opponent\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut at the same time, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m really focused on myself.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2772}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m always just trying to be a better athlete and then I just hope it will bring something nice to be battling with her.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Bol said Rome had been a useful stepping stone towards the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 3001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2942, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"score\": 0.9992652442687585, \"rank\": 0.0006890815703906586, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"a better athlete\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"her.\\u00e2\\u0080\